Package lazyTrees

Class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • lazyTrees.LazySearchTree<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - genetic type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable
    public class LazySearchTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    LazySearchTree is a Binary Search Tree (BST) algorithm that implements lazy deletion to solve the assigned tasks. This is an optimized version including collectGarbage() method to clean up the tree with hard deletion.
